sql_json.natural_language: Show me threads where administration@midlandsmeander.co.za is involved and the tone sounds urgent.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE 'administration@midlandsmeander.co.za' IN UNNEST(allEmails) AND (LOWER(subject) LIKE '%urgent%' OR LOWER(snippet) LIKE '%urgent%') ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
